languages.text: [Снять с руки перстень] "Вот знак моего благоволения, Вистенца. Пусть все видят, что ты заслужила мое доверие и находишься на особом положении".

traits.locale_text: [Снять с руки перстень] "Вот знак моего благоволения, Вистенца. Пусть все видят, что ты заслужила мое доверие и находишься на особом положении".

languages.text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [Quitarte el anillo de un dedo] «Esto es una muestra de mi favor, Vistenza. Que cuantos lo vean sepan que se ha ganado mi confianza y que ocupa un lugar especial entre mis súbditos nobles».
languages.original_text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [手から指輪をはずす]「これは我が恩恵の印だ、ヴィステンツァ。これを見た者すべてに、お前が{mf|俺|私}の信頼を得ており、高貴な臣民の中でも特別な地位を占めていることを知らしめるだろう」
languages.original_text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [从手上摘下戒指]“这枚戒指象征着我对你的青睐，维丝坦萨。所有看到这枚戒指的人都会明白——你已经赢得了我的信任，在我的贵族臣民之中脱颖而出。”
languages.original_text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [Einen Ring von deiner Hand ziehen] "Das ist ein Zeichen meiner Gunst, Vistenza. Alle, die es sehen, sollen wissen, dass Ihr mein Vertrauen und unter meinen adeligen Untertanen eine Sonderstellung genießt."
languages.original_text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [Retirer un de vos anneaux] « Voici un gage de mes faveurs, Vistenza. Que tous ceux qui voient cet anneau sachent que vous avez gagné ma confiance, et que vous occupez une place particulière parmi mes nobles sujets. »
languages.original_text: [Remove a ring from your hand] "This is a token of my favour, Vistenza. Let all who see it know that you have earned my trust and occupy a special position among my noble subjects."

languages.text: [Elindeki yüzüklerden birini çıkar] "Bu, tanıdığım imtiyazın bir simgesidir Vistenza. Onu gören herkes bilsin ki güvenimi kazanmayı başardın ve soylu tebaam arasında özel bir konuma sahipsin."
